-- GM board has concluded bankruptcy not an option
-- 
-- Thu Dec 11, 2008 6:59pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/11/us-gm-bankruptcy-idUSTRE4BA7LV20081211

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - General Motors Corp said on Thursday that its board has considered bankruptcy and concluded it is not a "viable option". 

 Highlight: * Says board meeting frequently, considering all options for company * Says board has 'retained appropriate advisers for all contingencies' * Spokesman declines to name advisers retained by automaker's board (Reporting by  Kevin Krolicki )